OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1783669804
OL,3,CMinister orders research into economic
OL,4,Cbenefits of Irish language in NI
OL,6,FStormont's Economy Minister Caoimhe
OL,7,FArchibald has commissioned research
OL,8,Finto the growth potential of the Irish
OL,9,Flanguage, "to inform future decisions
OL,10,Fon public expenditure".
OL,12,FThe two pieces of independent work,
OL,13,Fcalled for by the Sinn Fein minister
OL,14,Fand being conducted by Queen's
OL,15,FUniversity Belfast, will look at
OL,16,Feconomic impact as well as potential
OL,17,Fsupport for an Irish medium workforce.
OL,26,@qD@KOUrD@VO]uD@Yrr
