OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1783669804
OL,3,CMinister orders research into economic
OL,4,Cbenefits of Irish language in NI
OL,6,F"The development of the Irish-language
OL,7,Fsector in Northern Ireland
OL,8,Fdemonstrates that investment in social
OL,9,Finfrastructure for Irish speakers and
OL,10,Flearners delivers tangible benefits,
OL,11,Fattracting additional capital
OL,12,Finvestment and contributing to
OL,13,Fimproved educational outcomes," he
OL,14,Fsaid.
OL,16,F"These benefits, in turn, generate
OL,17,Fwider economic returns.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@_O]xD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/7
