PN,41904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1783669804
OL,3,CMinister orders research into economic
OL,4,Cbenefits of Irish language in NI
OL,6,F"This research should therefore
OL,7,Fprovide a robust evidence base to
OL,8,Finform future decisions on public
OL,9,Fexpenditure."
OL,11,FMs Archibald said: "There is growing
OL,12,Frecognition of the cultural and social
OL,13,Fvalue of the Irish language.
OL,15,F"However, less attention has been paid
OL,16,Fto its economic potential, both as a
OL,17,Fdriver of local regeneration and as a
OL,18,Fcontributor to wider economic growth.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@MO]sD@TOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/7
