PN,41905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1783669804
OL,3,CMinister orders research into economic
OL,4,Cbenefits of Irish language in NI
OL,6,F"This research will help inform policy
OL,7,Fdecisions to support good jobs and
OL,8,Fskills development and lead to broader
OL,9,Fconversations as our society becomes
OL,10,Fmore integrated and inclusive.
OL,12,F"The first piece of research is
OL,13,Fexpected to be launched in autumn 2026
OL,14,Fand the second in spring 2027."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUvD@_O]
