PN,41906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1783669804
OL,3,CMinister orders research into economic
OL,4,Cbenefits of Irish language in NI
OL,6,FOne project will be an economic impact
OL,7,Fassessment of the Irish language that
OL,8,Fwill aim to "quantify the direct and
OL,9,Findirect contribution of the Irish
OL,10,Flanguage to economic activity and
OL,11,Fprovide an evidence base for future
OL,12,Finvestment and policy decisions".
OL,14,FIt will also consider how to maximise
OL,15,Fthe economic potential of other
OL,16,Fminority languages.
OL,26,@pD@MOUtD@`O]
