OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1783669804
OL,3,CMinister orders research into economic
OL,4,Cbenefits of Irish language in NI
OL,6,FThe second piece of work on developing
OL,7,Fan Irish medium economy and workforce
OL,8,Fwill assess the effectiveness of the
OL,9,Fexisting mentoring and capacity-
OL,10,Fbuilding programme of An Meitheal
OL,11,FMeantoireachta, a mentoring and
OL,12,Ftraining programme run through Fis an
OL,13,FPhobail.
